        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I run a small agency. Between client calls, prospecting, and actually doing the work, my phone becomes a battlefield by 10 a.m. Every missed call is a missed invoice. That realization hit hard after I lost a $4,200 project because the prospect called while I was on another line and went straight to voicemail. They hired someone else that afternoon.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-answering-service-care"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's when I started looking seriously at ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Answering Service Care",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Not a robotic auto-attendant. Not a chatbot pretending to care. Real, US-based human agents who pick up the phone 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, and talk to your callers like they work in your office.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's everything I've learned — and the tips I wish someone had given me on day one.",
